subSubSection.paragraph:
Parapronoe

appears to be widely distributed in tropical and temperate regions of the world’s oceans. 

Parapronoe elongata

is a relatively rare species, and is only known from the Tasman Sea (
Semenova 1981
), the Coral Sea (
Zeidler 1998
) and the China Sea (
Shih & Chen 1995
).
